        <Text><![CDATA[*Do not move the headset away from the PC or pull out the USB transceiver.
*Be sure not to perform updates in an environment where there is a large quantity of 2.4 GHz band radio waves emitted from sources such as Wi-Fi, microwaves, cordless telephones, etc.


※ Sony | INZONE Hub ※
Please update to the latest version before updating the main unit

[Update details in version 1.2.5]
- Quality improvement of voice commands sent to the opposite party

[Notes]
1) Perform updates only after closing unnecessary software on the PC.
2) If connected to a laptop PC, perform updates after confirming it is connected to a power source.
3) Be sure not to let the PC enter sleep mode or hibernation mode during update.

[How to check the software version]
Select device settings on the upper-left area of the Sony | INZONE Hub app screen and make confirmations on the system software information.


